This paper belongs to the Natural Language Processing (NLP) domain of Computer Science, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv. The use of case-based reasoning (CBR) for weather forecast text generation suggests that this paper is likely to be classified under cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-category. Additionally, the use of machine learning techniques such as CBR also suggests that this paper could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval and text summarization, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves the development of a system, which could place it under cs.SD (Software Engineering) sub-category.
